.so man1/sci.an
.SH NAME
gbruit - noise generation 
.SH DESCRIPTION
[]=gbruit(pas,Tmax,sig)

generates a Scilab macro [b]=bruit(t)
where bruit(t) is a piecewise constant function 
( constant on  [k*pas,(k+1)*pas] ). The value on each constant 
interval are random values from  i.i.d  Gaussian variables of 
standard deviation sig. The function is constant fo t<=0 and 
t>=Tmax.
